### Phase 1 — Schema and Hash Capture

**Goal:** Record SHA-256 hashes of generated artifacts in the database. No behavior change for existing callers. Hashes become available for future integrity checking.

**Cursor prompt:**

```
You are implementing Phase 1 of the cloud-deploy thick-client API foundation for Lumiverb.

## Goal
Add SHA-256 hash columns to the database and populate them when proxies are generated.
No existing behavior changes. All existing tests must continue to pass.

## Files to modify

