  - ADD COLUMN thumbnail_sha256 TEXT to the assets table (nullable, no default)
  - ADD COLUMN rep_frame_sha256 TEXT to the video_scenes table (nullable, no default)
  - Downgrade must DROP those columns.

### 2. src/models/tenant.py — Asset model
Add to the Asset class:
